const internshipsInfo = [
    {
        key: 1,
        internRole: "Data Analytics Intern (Digital Marketing & E-Commerce)",
        company: "Marina Bay Sands | Las Vegas Sands Corporation",
        date: "July 2022 - December 2022",
        description: ["Automated report generation using Python and successfully increased efficiency in 2 weekly performance reports, with data extracted from Google Analytics.",
                        "Designed and implemented complete ETL data pipelines to extract large datasets from Microsoft SQL Server, and performed data cleaning, transformation, and enrichment for machine learning models and Tableau data visualization reports.",
                        "Developed a K nearest neighbor clustering model to identify customer clusters for targeted marketing campaigns.",
                        "Analysed audience performance data throughout the c ustomer journey across the marketing tech stack (Customer Data Platform) to optimise customer journey.",
                        "Collaborated with the different marketing teams to optimise conversion rates and KPIs through data analysis across channels such as media, website and mobile."
                    ],
        url: "https://www.marinabaysands.com"
    },

    {
        key: 2,
        internRole: "Data Science Intern",
        company: "RSM Singapore",
        date: "December 2021 - May 2022",
        description: ["Built an application collaboratively using Python and SQL, with a focus on developing the frontend using Tkinter and Figma. The application serves as an internal portal for managers to track prospects and updates.",
                        "Developed a 2-day Python workshop for finance professionals, covering fundamental Python concepts, web scraping using Python, and automated report generation for P&L analysis.",
                        "Conducted a 2-day data processing and BI tools training program for audit professionals, providing instruction on data analysis tools such as Knime and PowerBI.",
                        "Collaborated on a Python project on GitHub that successfully auto generates lease liability reports for auditors, greatly increasing efficiency in their client report generation.",
                        "Developed a Python script that automates QR code generation to simplify payment processing by enabling efficient distribution of payment QR codes to clients."],
        url: "https://www.rsm.global/singapore/service/data-science"
    },

    {
        key: 3,
        internRole: "Junior Analyst Member",
        company: "NUS Business Analytics Consulting Team",
        date: "August 2021 - April 2022",
        description: ["Learnt techniques on machine learning, data visualisation and web automation.", 
                    "Partnered with Pan-Malayan to build dashboards for their analytical purposes."],
        url: "https://www.linkedin.com/company/nusbact/"
    },

    {
        key: 4,
        internRole: "Data Analytics Intern",
        company: "Stone Forest Singapore",
        date: "May 2021 - August 2021",
        description: ["Generated P&L dashboards and reports using Spotlight Reporting",
                    "Took on the main role of evaluating the functionality of Spotlight Reporting and how much it can value-add to the reports for clients."],
        url: "https://www.stoneforest.com.sg/"
    },

    {
        key: 5,
        internRole: "Digital Marketing and Retail Operations Intern",
        company: "Weekend Sundries",
        date: "February 2019 - April 2019",
        description: ["Involved in the ideation and execution of marketing campaigns.",
                    "Created Social Media content for the brand.",
                    "Assisted in retail operations."],
        url: "https://weekendsundries.com/"
    },

    {
        key: 6,
        internRole: "Business Analyst - WorkPass 2.0",
        company: "GovTech | Ministry of Manpower",
        date: "June 2023 - October 2023",
        description: ["Incoming internship"],
        url: "https://www.tech.gov.sg/"
    }
]
